ConfigOpus - ChangeLog:
-----------------------

2006-09-19 - ConfigOpus 4.17.8
* ConfigOpus now longer crashes when you clear a hotkey with right mouse
button.

2006-09-24 - ConfigOpus 4.17.9
* Extract command added.

2006-10-01 - ConfigOpus 4.17.10
* Changed some of the old requesters into IDOS->TimedDosRequester().

2007-01-11 - ConfigOpus 4.18.1
* Small fix to System->Icons part. Doesn't give a DSI anymore, and shows
the '*' part for the three default icons, if icons are chosen by the user.

2015-02-13 - config-os4/ConfigOpus_rev.h (ConfigOpus 4.18.2)
* Updated version (subrevisions) for next release.
+ Committed revision 570.

2015-02-22 - config-os4/gadgets.c
* Disabled hidden protection bit option. H bit is actually hold bit.
+ Committed revision 576.

***Released archive of repository revision 578. (DirectoryOpus 4.18.41)

2015-03-27 - All header files (xxx.h) - config-os4/dopusiff.h
* Moved duplicated iff definitions to added include-os4/dopusiff.h
* Removed config-os4/dopusiff.h
* Added missing pragma pack directives to all header files.
+ Committed revision 579.

***Released archive of repository revision 582. (DirectoryOpus 4.18.42)
***Released archive of repository revision 590. (DirectoryOpus 4.18.43)

2015-04-28 - config-os4/Makefile
* Improved ConfigOpus makefile.
+ Committed revision 591.

2015-05-05 - config-os4/#?
* Replaced all AllocMem() and FreeMem() function calls with AllocVec()
  and FreeVec() function calls.
+ Committed revision 593.

2015-05-08 - config-os4/#?
* Replaced all deprecated memory allocation functions with Dopus4
  functions that use the OS4 AllocvecTags() function.
* Modified makefile to make compiler text output more readable.
+ Committed revision 594.

2015-06-16 config-os4/#? include-os4/dopus/config.h
* Fixed all compiler warnings with added type-casting and changing some
  structure & variable declarations to match function arg declarations.
* Replaced all unbounded string functions and dopus.library string functions
  with size limited C library string functions. (strlcpy, snprintf etc.)
+ Committed revision 605.

